PrecisGrant to the City of North York, for a term of forty-nine (49) years, of two easements and one right-of-way which will encumber the property situate at 4900 Yonge Street, in the City of North York, Ontario, in order to provide for pedestrian connections between the Government of Canada Building, the Madison Centre and the Sheppard Centre.
